node.text:
Holiday shoppin’ #bourbon style 🎁🥃! Our own Seth Thompson is here to guide you through the @buffalotracedistillery Gift Shop experience, a brand new Covid safe bourbon haven! Curbside pickup is available. Check out their website for the goods: http://buffalotrace.me/bourbonreview 

Here’s to a safe and happy holiday🎁🥃
.
.
.
#bourbon #bourbonwhiskey #buffalotracedistillery #holidayseason #holidayshopping  #cigar #yeti #eaglerare #buffalotrace #kentucky #kentuckybourbon #bourboncountry

node.title: Holiday Shoppin’ at Buffalo Trace Distillery

node.text:
It’s National Ice Cream Day!🎉 To celebrate, here’s some to die for Bourbon Smoked Soy Caramel Sauce, recipe in our bio link. Cheers y’all🥃 Goodness from @bourbonbarrelfoods
.
.
.
#nationalicecreamday #nationalicecreammonth #caramel #bourbonbarrelfoods #icecream #bourbon #bourboncountry #gobourbon #thebourbonreview #bourbonreview

node.text:
“Bourbon Shortbread Cookies”. Buttery. Crumbly. Deliciousness. Your weekend calls for awesomeness!🥃
Recipe in our bio link.
.
📸 and recipe: @thegandmkitchen
.
.
.
#bourbon #recipes #gourmetcookies #gourmet #weekend #weekendvibes #bourboncountry #gobourbon #thebourbonreview

.

node.text: We got an advance screening of tomorrow’s upcoming @netflix docu-series “Heist,” featuring the famous #Pappygate - and all we have to say is, clear your #whiskeywednesday. “Heist” begins streaming July 14th - link in bio and story for our review 🥃
